b'Asatir: Mirai no Mukashi Banashi': b"In 2050 Riyadh, elder Asma's richly captivating storytelling transports her cherished grandchildren to fabled times where they learn that modern-day dilemmas are no match for the trials, tribulations and words of wisdom passed from generation to generation through their fascinating folktales.\n\n(Source: Sentai Filmworks)"
